{
  "stem": "27507.8",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know exactly how it happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Suddenly, it was announced that the whole population of ghetto, whoever remained, was going to assemble in a very small area near [POLISH] Street, and in a number of blocks of houses around in [POLISH] Street, in the north of the ghetto, not far from the Umschlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that there is going to be another selection.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everybody had to be there with their small amount of belongings, and so on, at 10:00 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At 10:00 o'clock, the [POLISH] area, all of this, and the rest of the ghetto, all had to be empty of people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember again, this morning was-- again, everybody was panic-stricken.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there were still many, many people pushing their little carts, and running this way and that way, like frightened animals, not knowing which way to go, and which way to-- but we-- that means my parents, my uncles, and so on-- nobody wanted to go to this [POLISH] Street, because nobody saw anything that there was-- everybody saw that it might be impossible to get rescued from there.",
      "word_count": 69
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we decided to stay behind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we tried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was not easy to stay behind, because the place where we-- the cellar where we hid in on my birthday, somebody else was there already.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we tried to get into some bunker.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was completely full.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So there was no way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we finally, all of us, that means my uncles, and aunts, and my parents, and myself, about all together-- not all of them, but about 10 people, or maybe 12 people-- we all hid behind some kind of a very basic partition.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
